post_text:
The following message is from the Kiowa County Schools Yearbook staff.

Due to COVID-19, we are having to make several changes in our yearbook. The yearbook staff would like your help. We would like you to email us pictures that represent your daily life during this unprecedented time. This could include at-home learning, outdoor activities, Zoom classes, family fun, etc. Please add a description for each of your pictures. Pictures off of phones need to be emailed at actual size. Please send your emails to yearbook@usd422.org.

Thank you,

Katie Spainhour, Yearbook Editor
